stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> WAITING
    WAITING --> RECORDING : 音量 > VOICE_THRESHOLD
    RECORDING --> PROCESSING_STT : 静音超时 或 缓冲满
    RECORDING --> WAITING : 录音 < 0.8s (噪音过滤)
    PROCESSING_STT --> PROCESSING_LLM : STT 识别成功
    PROCESSING_STT --> WAITING : STT 失败
    PROCESSING_LLM --> PROCESSING_TTS : DeepSeek 返回成功
    PROCESSING_LLM --> WAITING : LLM 错误
    PROCESSING_TTS --> PLAYBACK : TTS 下载成功
    PROCESSING_TTS --> WAITING : TTS 失败
    PLAYBACK --> WAITING : 播放完成
